OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Food and Drug Administration (FDA),
OL,6, which regulates medical products in the
OL,7, US, has approved an e-cigarette  for   
OL,8, sale for the first time.               
OL,10,FIt authorised the marketing of three   
OL,11,Fproducts from RJ Reynolds, under the   
OL,12,FVuse brand.                            
OL,14,FThe FDA decided that the benefit to    
OL,15,Fadults trying to quit smoking outweighs
OL,16,Fthe risk of teenagers becoming hooked. 
OL,18,FThe permitted products are             
OL,19,Ftobacco-flavoured, as opposed to the   
OL,20,Fsweet flavours popular with younger    
OL,21,Fpeople.                                
